It is a super simple cocktail that is refreshing and perfect for a chilled weekend with friends. Ingredients Preparation Step 1 Add the juice of two wedges of lime to two glasses along with a tablespoon of sugar. Step 2 Muddle the strawberries with the back of a spoon in the glasses until the sugar is mostly dissolved. Step 3 Add ice, three ounces of gin to each glass, and fill the glass to the top with club soda. Enjoy!